sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Pacman
    participant Pel as PowerPellet
    participant GM as GameManager
    participant SM as ScoreManager
    participant G as Ghost[]
    participant F as GhostFrightened

    Note over P,F: Power Pellet eaten sequence

    P->>Pel: OnTriggerEnter2D (Pacman layer)
    Pel->>Pel: Eat()
    Pel->>GM: PowerPelletEaten(this)

    loop For each ghost
        GM->>G: frightened.Enable(pellet.duration)
        G->>F: Enable(duration)
        F->>F: body off, blue on, eyes off
        F->>G: movement.speedMultiplier = 0.5
        F->>F: Invoke(Flash, duration/2)
        F->>F: Invoke(Disable, duration)
    end

    GM->>GM: OnPowerPelletEatenEvent?.Invoke(pellet)
    GM->>GM: PelletEaten(pellet)
    GM->>Pel: gameObject.SetActive(false)
    GM->>SM: Add(pellet.points)
    GM->>GM: CancelInvoke(ResetGhostMultiplier)
    GM->>GM: Invoke(ResetGhostMultiplier, pellet.duration)

    Note over GM,F: After duration: Flash (blue->white), then Disable<br/>restores sprites and speedMultiplier = 1
